    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200°C/ 180°C (fan)/ 395°F/ Gas 6</p><p>Peel and finely slice the <strong>shallot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Top, tail and grate the <strong>carrot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p>",
