    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop the root<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> from the<strong> little gem lettuce</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>and tear the <strong>leaves</strong> into rough, bite-sized pieces and give them a wash</p><p>Combine the<strong> red wine vinegar</strong> with the<strong> Dijon mustard</strong> and 2 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [4 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>– this is your<strong> vinaigrette</strong></p>",
